      "text": "St Gen Choir - Easter (A) Search this site Embedded Files Skip to main content Skip to navigation St Gen Choir Pentecost Easter (A) Mass of Christ Savior St Gen Choir Pentecost Easter (A) Mass of Christ Savior More Pentecost Easter (A) Mass of Christ Savior Easter (A) 7 th Sunday of Easter (A) May 1 7 ALL PDFs Entrance: Canticle of the Sun Haugen Psalm: I believe I shall see the…. R&A Offertory: We are many parts Haugen Communion: We Remember Recessional: Go out, Go out Stephen Go to Pentecost First Sun of Easter ALL PDFs Entrance: Jesus Christ is Risen today Mass parts Mass of St. Ann Sequence: Christ is Arisen Randall DeBryun Sprinkling Rite: You Will Draw Water Joyfully Tony Alonso Preparation of the gifts: This is The Day Michael Joncas Communion: Worthy is the Lamb Recessional: Join in The Dance April 12, 2026 Second Sunday of Easter (A) All PDFs ENTRANCE: Join in the Dance - Schutte PREPARATION OF GIFTS: Peace I Leave to You - B. Bridge COMMUNION: Hold on to love - Manibusan RECESSIONAL: This Day was made by the Lord - Walker Optional : Divine Mercy April 19, 2026 Third Sunday of Easter (A) ALL PDFs ENTRANCE: Alleluia, Love is Alive! PREPARATION OF GIFTS: Christ the Lord COMMUNION: The Supper of the Lord RECESSIONAL: Regina Caeli Chant/ Vatican The Day of Resurrection - Ellacombe 4th Sunday of Easter (A) April 26, 2026 ALL PDFs Entrance: Sing a Joyful Song Preparation of the gifts: Eye has Not Seen Haugen Communion: Because the Lord is My Shepherd Walker As Christ is for Us Recessional: Regina Caeli Chant/ Vatican 5th Sunday of Easter (A) May 03 ALL PDFs Entrance: Jesus is Risen Lasst Uns Erfreuen Psalm: Lord, Let your mercy be on us R&A Offertory: I am the bread of Life Angrisano/ Tom Booth Communion: O God, You Search Me Farrell Recessional: Regina Caeli Chant/ Vatican 6th Sunday of Easter (A) May 10 ALL PDFs The Prayer PDF (change lyrics to A mothers Prayer by Celion Dion) Entrance: Alleluia, Sing to Jesus Hyfrydol Psalm: Let all the earth Cry out to God R&A Offertory: Only in God Talbot Communion: Eat This Bread Berthier Come to me and Drink Bob Hurd Mothers day Song: More than enough Recessional: Regina Caeli Chant/ Vatican Contents of this website is solely for St. Genevieve Choir. Google Sites Report abuse Page details Page updated Google Sites Report abuse",
